@startuml seq-instant-overlay-snapshot
'' Sequence: instant, flash-free overlay compositing over the always-on-top web view.
'' The in-app web view is a main-owned WebContentsView that always paints ABOVE the renderer DOM, so a
'' DOM menu / context-menu / dialog / palette cannot draw over it. Main PROACTIVELY captures the live page
'' to a JPEG raster (after load + debounced on scroll-settle) and PUSHES it to the renderer
'' (vv:http-snapshot-ready); web-host caches it, so opening ANY overlay is a SYNCHRONOUS DOM swap to the
'' frozen image + hide the native view — instant, no behind-then-front flash, never blank. The live view
'' is restored on close. Unified: dialogs freeze the (dimmed) page too, instead of going blank.
'' (PlantUML over Mermaid: participant colouring + activation lanes for the capture→push→freeze handoff.)
!include _vv-theme.iuml

title Instant overlay compositing over the web view (pre-cached pushed snapshot)

actor User
participant "main\nweb.cljs (web view)" as WEB #3A5BA0
participant "preload\nonHttpSnapshotReady" as IPC #B1951D
participant "web-host\n(.vv-web-host)" as HOST #2D9574
participant ":ui/overlay-open?\n(app-db)" as DB #7590DB

== Proactive capture — page live + visible ==
WEB -> WEB : did-stop-loading / scroll-settle\n→ capture-soon! (debounced 150 ms)
activate WEB
WEB -> WEB : capturePage → toJPEG(70)\n→ data:image/jpeg data-URL
WEB -> IPC : vv:http-snapshot-ready (data-URL)
deactivate WEB
IPC -> HOST : onHttpSnapshotReady
activate HOST
HOST -> HOST : cache in pre-snap (atom)\n— no DOM change yet
deactivate HOST

== Overlay opens — menu / context-menu / dialog / palette ==
User -> DB : open a menu or modal
DB -> HOST : :ui/overlay-open? = true
activate HOST
HOST -> HOST : freeze! — (reset! snap @pre-snap)\n→ render <img.vv-web-snap>
HOST -> WEB : vv:http-hide (httpHide)
WEB -> WEB : setVisible false\n(native view hidden)
note over HOST #FFF6D6 : INSTANT synchronous swap — the frozen page shows\nunder the overlay; no capture on this path, no flash,\nnever blank (a dialog dims it via its backdrop).\nCold start (no push yet): freeze! pulls main's cache\nvia the vv:http-snapshot invoke, then hides.
deactivate HOST

== Overlay closes ==
User -> DB : close the overlay
DB -> HOST : :ui/overlay-open? = false
activate HOST
HOST -> HOST : (reset! snap nil) — drop the still
HOST -> WEB : vv:http-show (httpShow url + bounds)
WEB -> WEB : setVisible true\n(live, scrollable page restored)
deactivate HOST
@enduml
